From: pr-b
Subject: [PATCH] docs: add autopickup command to commands table

Adds a new row for the `autopickup every N min` command. Pure additive — appends
one row at the bottom of the commands table. Conflicts with pr-a-diff.patch
because both patches append a new line at the same position in the table.

---
 base-commands-table.md | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/base-commands-table.md b/base-commands-table.md
--- a/base-commands-table.md
+++ b/base-commands-table.md
@@ -12,3 +12,4 @@
 | `pick up #42` | Spawn `worker-implementation` on that specific ticket |
 | `review PR #501` | Spawn `worker-review` on that PR |
 | `test discover <repo>` | Spawn `worker-test-discovery` on that repo |
+| `autopickup every N min` | Enter scheduled auto-pickup mode (N clamped to [5, 120], default 30). |
